                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18221023-83-off454 t18221023-83-cd455"></join>, 28 lbs. of sugar, value 12 s.; 1 lb. of raisins, value 6 d.; 8 oz. of currants, value 6 d.; 4 oz. of tea, value 1 s. 9 d. and one bag, value 6 d.
            </rs> the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18221023-83-victim916" type="victimName">
                     John 
